# Gmail mailboxes:
# "[Gmail]/Todos"
# "[Gmail]/Borradores"
# "[Gmail]/Importantes"
# "[Gmail]/Enviados"
# "[Gmail]/Spam"
# "[Gmail]/Destacados"
# "[Gmail]/Papelera"

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
User vastagox@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmailapp/vastagox"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/email/gmail/
INBOX ~/.local/share/email/gmail/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "[Gmail]/Importantes" "[Gmail]/Destacados" "[Gmail]/Enviados" "[Gmail]/Spam"  
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both
MaxMessages 0
